metadata.description: The Last Gutter Supper depicts the moment that Cliff (center cat) reveals to his crew that one of them will betray the gang. The artist, in one still image, captures a complex range of reactions to this shocking news. Gutter scholars have long debated who at the table is the snitch. But come on, we all know it was one of the rats.
metadata.name: Last Gutter Supper
